{"tid":419400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"街頭留假聯絡成功騙款3800　49歲男疑人旺角落網","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T13:09:28.000Z","uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a28504bfc32aca44ea24e9dfd91c054799b35da6","tid":419400,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:48:35.000Z","msg":"警方8月至今共接獲5宗報案，指一名男子在街頭向報案人訛稱失去個人財物，向他們借取金錢及留下虛假聯絡方法後逃去，初步調查顯示涉案金額達3800元。<br />\n<br />\n旺角警區刑事調查隊人員經調查後，昨（29日）晚約8時，在旺角區拘捕一名49歲姓梁本地男子，涉嫌以欺騙手段取得財產。該被捕男子正被扣留調查，以及是否與其他同類案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民，如曾遭人用類似手法行騙或有資料提供，請致電3661 8715與6101 0346與警方聯絡。另市民若在街上遇到有人藉詞接近，除非已確定對方真正身份及聯絡方法，否則切勿輕信及借錢予陌生人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00001/1506774082022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F1506774082022&d=H7Y15nXf66iWyqF3UxDF9UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=1cda78c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170930%2Fs00001%2F1506774082022&h=643b0e31\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170930/s00001/1506774082022</a><br />\n個廢中都唔知搵埋搵埋賺咗幾多先比人拉咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c7fc2f06e400a5688558673a0eb28802bc86fe3","tid":419400,"uid":73,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:00:45.000Z","msg":"警方呼籲市民，如曾遭人用類似手法行騙或有資料提供，請致電3661 8715與6101 0346<br />\n<br />\n聯絡警方有手提no. 咁得意"},{"pid":"8ac784a3b99df3218566537bb943f898657b1a07","tid":419400,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T13:09:28.000Z","msg":"叫我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}